        Opens or creates a TileContainer at the specified location that will be able to
        Parameters:
        path - The path of the target tile container
        spec - Describes the layout of the target tile container, may not be null
        hint - The desired provider, or null to select any compatible container provider
        Returns:

      • open

        public static TileContainer open​(java.lang.String path,
                                 boolean readOnly,
                                 java.lang.String hint)
        Opens an already existing tile container at the specified location.
        Parameters:
        path - The path
        readOnly - true to open as read-only, false to allow read-write.
        hint - The desired provider, or null to select any container provider that can open the file at specified location.
        Returns:
        A new TileContainer instance providing access to the tile content at the specified location or null if no such container could be opened.
